					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I have nothing to contribute to the topic - what little composition I have done is entirely instinctive or 'by ear' - but I'd like to direct anyone interested in hearing more of Yuzo Koshiro's work to <a href="http://vgmrips.net/packs/composer/yuzo-koshiro" class="postlink">VGMRips</a> and <a href="http://project2612.org/search.php?query=Yuzo+Koshiro&amp;field=composer&amp;submit=Search" class="postlink">Project 2612</a>. If you're interested in FM you can even crack open the VGMs and see how it was done.<br /><br />...actually, on second thoughts, I do have some advice: learn an instrument, if you haven't already. Goofing around playing random notes and melodies can be inspiring, assuming you can write them down.</div>

